#: .\pinmok\cmfadmin\templates\admin\url_alias_tip.html:9
msgid "URL Alias Feature Setup"
msgstr "URL 别名功能配置"

#: .\pinmok\cmfadmin\templates\admin\url_alias_tip.html:12
msgid ""
"To enable the URL alias feature, you need to add one line to your project's "
"root urls.py file. Without this, aliases will be saved but will not work."
msgstr "要启用 URL 别名功能，需要在项目根 urls.py 文件中添加一行代码。若不添加，别名将被保存但不会生效。"

#: .\pinmok\cmfadmin\templates\admin\url_alias_tip.html:14
msgid "Step 1: Import the view"
msgstr "第一步：导入视图"

#: .\pinmok\cmfadmin\templates\admin\url_alias_tip.html:15
msgid "Add the following import at the top of your root urls.py:"
msgstr "在根 urls.py 顶部添加以下导入："

#: .\pinmok\cmfadmin\templates\admin\url_alias_tip.html:19
msgid "Step 2: Add the URL pattern"
msgstr "第二步：添加 URL 定义"

#: .\pinmok\cmfadmin\templates\admin\url_alias_tip.html:20
msgid ""
"Add the following line inside your urlpatterns list. It must be the last "
"item, after all other patterns:"
msgstr "在 urlpatterns 列表中添加以下行，必须放在所有其他定义的最后："

#: .\pinmok\cmfadmin\templates\admin\url_alias_tip.html:24
msgid "Complete example"
msgstr "完整示例"

#: .\pinmok\cmfadmin\templates\admin\url_alias_tip.html:25
msgid "Your urls.py should look like this:"
msgstr "您的 urls.py 应如下所示："

#: .\pinmok\cmfadmin\templates\admin\url_alias_tip.html:41
msgid "Why must it be last?"
msgstr "为什么必须放在最后？"

#: .\pinmok\cmfadmin\templates\admin\url_alias_tip.html:43
msgid ""
"Django matches URL patterns in order, from top to bottom. The alias pattern "
"matches any URL, so if it is placed before other patterns, it will intercept"
" all requests and your site will stop working correctly. Always keep it as "
"the last item in urlpatterns."
msgstr ""
"Django 按从上到下的顺序匹配 URL 定义。别名定义可匹配任意 URL，若放在其他模式之前，将会拦截所有请求，导致站点无法正常运行。"
"因此需始终将其放在 urlpatterns 的最后。"

#: .\pinmok\cmfadmin\templates\admin\url_alias_tip.html:50
msgid "How does it work?"
msgstr "它是如何工作的？"

#: .\pinmok\cmfadmin\templates\admin\url_alias_tip.html:52
msgid ""
"When a visitor accesses an alias URL (e.g. /news/), Django first tries to "
"match all regular URL patterns. If none match, the alias resolver checks the"
" alias table. If a matching alias is found and is active, the request is "
"forwarded internally to the real URL. The visitor's browser address bar "
"keeps showing the alias URL."
msgstr ""
"当用户访问别名 URL（如 /news/）时，Django 首先尝试匹配所有常规 URL 模式。若均不匹配，别名解析器将检查别名表。"
"若找到匹配的有效别名，请求将被内部转发至真实 URL，用户浏览器地址栏仍显示别名 URL。"

#: .\pinmok\cmfadmin\templates\admin\url_alias_tip.html:59
msgid ""
"After adding the line to urls.py, restart your development server. The "
"warning on this page will disappear automatically once the configuration is "
"detected."
msgstr "在 urls.py 中添加该行后，重启开发服务器。检测到正确配置后，此页面的警告将自动消失。"

#: .\pinmok\cmfadmin\templates\admin\url_alias_tip.html:62
msgid ""
"Make sure there are no duplicate aliases. If two aliases are identical, only"
" the first one saved will be used. The second one will cause a validation "
"error when you try to save it."
msgstr "请确保没有重复的别名。若两个别名相同，仅第一个保存的别名生效，保存第二个时将触发验证错误。"

